  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-engine chess analysis with UCI support",
    "Game import from Lichess, Chess.com, and PGN files",
    "Opening repertoire training with spaced repetition",
    "Exact and partial position search",
    "Adaptive puzzle system with custom Elo rating",
    "Comprehensive player statistics and performance tracking",
    "Pawn structure analysis and classification",
    "Cross-platform support (Windows, macOS, Linux, Android)",
    "Local SQLite database with data ownership",
    "Multi-profile system with account integration"
